graph TD
    Root[Agent Memory Systems]

    %% Short-term memory branch
    Root --> STM[Short-Term Memory]
    STM --> Working[Working Memory]
    Working --> WorkingDesc["Limited capacity<br/>Conversation history<br/>Persists across LLM calls"]

    %% Long-term memory branch
    Root --> LTM[Long-Term Memory]

    LTM --> Episodic[Episodic Memory]
    Episodic --> EpisodicDesc["Specific events & experiences<br/>Agent actions & outcomes<br/>Example: Last birthday party"]

    LTM --> Semantic[Semantic Memory]
    Semantic --> SemanticDesc["Knowledge about the world<br/>External databases (Wikipedia)<br/>Example: Capital of France"]

    LTM --> Procedural[Procedural Memory]
    Procedural --> ProceduralDesc["Patterns & procedures<br/>System prompts<br/>Example: How to write Python"]

    %% Parametric memory (special case)
    Root --> Parametric[Parametric Memory]
    Parametric --> ParametricDesc["Model parameters<br/>Trained knowledge<br/>Instilled via fine-tuning"]

